rows.label: qst200505_msg001
rows.name:
You want to hear about
Alban's beached ship?

rows.label: qst200505_msg002
rows.name:
I was a navigation officer back
then. I was just starting out, too.

rows.label: qst200505_msg003
rows.name:
It was my first ever voyage. I still
recall how the ship lurched from side
to side...how my stomach was churning...

rows.label: qst200505_msg004
rows.name:
In fact, that's about the only
thing I remember. I was on the
verge of passing out...

rows.label: qst200505_msg005
rows.name:
Well anyway, we were heading out to
the Cloud Sea, of that I'm sure. I
threw up the moment we reached land...
